Revision history for Perl extension MarpaX::Languages::Lua::Parser.

1.05  2021-05-23T18:54:00
	- Adopt patches from Jeffrey Kegler which allow the parser to handle multi-line comments.
	- Change the format of the dates in this file.
	- Change licence from Artistic to Perl.
	- Reformat Makefile.PL. Add TEST_REQUIRES.
	- Add t/00.versions.t and t/00.versions.tx

1.04  2015-08-02T11:33:00
	- Incorporate grammar changes discussed here:
		https://github.com/ronsavage/MarpaX-Languages-Lua-Parser/issues/2 and
		https://github.com/ronsavage/MarpaX-Languages-Lua-Parser/issues/3.
	- Add lua.sources/constructs.lua from MarpaX::Languages::Lua::AST.
	- Add lua.output/constructs.txt. It's output from MarpaX::Languages::Lua::Parser.
	- Reformat grammar slightly, by replacing 4 leading spaces with a "\t".

1.03  2015-07-12T17:07:00
	- Update pre-reqs to Data::RenderAsTree V 1.03.

1.02  2015-07-12T14:52:00
	- Remove the line 'use open qw(:std :utf8);'. See RT#105798 (for Tree::DAG_Node actually).

1.01  2015-07-06T12:57:00
	- Bump pre-req for Data::RenderAsTree to V 1.02.

1.00  2015-06-15T09:46:00
	  - Original version